author: jruizvar
body:
The HLT SUSY validation code changed back in 2014. The last validation with the old code was 720pre5, and after that the HLT SUSY Validation moved to a new DQM code (#5693).

Deleting unused files is part of the maintenance of the current package.
title: Remove obsolete files in the HLT SUSY Validation package (forward port of #13460)
